  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EffectDescription
    A class describing a light representation of an effect provided by a weapon
    LoadedState
    State of a fully-loaded weapon which is ready to shoot.
    PickupState
    State of a weapon before being grabbed.
    UnloadedState
    State of a weapon which has just shot.
    WeaponCard
    A class describing a light representation of a weapon Holds information about: A textual description of the effects of the weapon, its reload cost and the additional cost for each effect.
    WeaponCardState
    Represents the state of a weapon card.
    WeaponCreator
    Static resource class which loads weapons from configuration file and makes them available as a service.
